{"tid":26302,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"好似有啲變態  短篇《親愛的》","createTime":"2016-12-06T15:49:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-12T12:17:08.000Z","uid":53185,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"113dcfc8589609f51bde732146e938dce976d38a","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:49:27.000Z","msg":"唔知幾時寫落嘅一篇文 其實唔算好長 但係都希望大家比啲意見我<br />\n<br />\n                              正文<br />\n<br />\n把妳的心臟掏空吧<br />\n我想看見妳的血流滿胸口<br />\n全身的血管都斷裂<br />\n手指的紋絡被血浸染<br />\n是別樣的美麗<br />\n鮮血從指尖滴落<br />\n在地面上開出了花<br />\n妳喜歡的對吧<br />\n眼珠滾落下來<br />\n別擔心<br />\n我會幫妳撿起來<br />\n味道很好<br />\n妳要嚐嚐嗎<br />\n看我多愛妳<br />\n等我咬碎了妳的眼珠<br />\n妳就不能再看他了<br />\n我迫不及待想讓他看見妳現在的樣子<br />\n那樣他會離開妳<br />\n在妳心裏消失<br />\n等我把妳整個人都吃掉<br />\n妳就會知道<br />\n誰才是真正愛妳<br />\n那些虛僞的人啊<br />\n他們不會知道<br />\n妳的血液在我身體裏流淌<br />\n親愛的<br />\n妳的血真甜<br />\n我最喜歡妳了<br />\n親愛的妳的胸口怎麼破了<br />\n我幫妳縫上<br />\n縫好了妳就是我一個人的<br />\n是他讓妳受傷的吧<br />\n別擔心<br />\n我會殺了他<br />\n把他的頭髮剪下來<br />\n編成花環送給妳<br />\n就像當初我送妳的一樣...<br />\n<br />\n有人睇再出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bacf50208b5c44f2c2bf3fb89f25610e8e8751db","tid":26302,"uid":30268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:51:24.000Z","msg":"好病態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3065c30029a9a1686bc6b871436a0cf20a123324","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好病態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實仲有啲未出 但係想多啲人睇嗰時再send上黎 同埋都希望各位可以比多啲意見我睇下有咩要改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca3fc320259ec93a9ce5f6fc22542c7a34002b1","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:56:37.000Z","msg":"咦<br />\n他的眼睛爲什麼不閉上呢<br />\n親愛的妳看這雙眼睛<br />\n真是醜惡到令人作嘔對吧<br />\n他經常這麼看妳嗎<br />\n真是惡毒的男人啊<br />\n他想拆散我們吧<br />\n那就挖了他的雙眼吧<br />\n正好親愛的妳缺不是嗎<br />\n這樣妳又可以看到我了<br />\n親愛的<br />\n我是真的愛妳啊<br />\n咦<br />\n他的眼珠爲什麼總是從妳的眼眶中滾落呢<br />\n我就知道你們不適合啊<br />\n那試試我的眼珠好嗎<br />\n刀子插進眼睛裏好痛啊<br />\n但一想到妳可以看見我<br />\n我就什麼都不怕了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出住咁多先 聽日再出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a65772b8ff8e07345175202d8dc2e784041fe5","tid":26302,"uid":51573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:07:10.000Z","msg":"呢篇寫得好過果篇喎lol<br />\n睇到有d 心寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然變態但勝在夠渲染力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055c74e2e5a25641b743e31ff052e3a4da294737","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:08:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢篇寫得好過果篇喎lol<br />\n睇到有d 心寒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然變態但勝在夠渲染力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />😂"},{"pid":"9effc22f007b8ad43a6828f0373896197ca51f62","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:26:19.000Z","msg":"哦<br />\n原來在這啊<br />\n眼珠沒有掉下來呢<br />\n果然我們是最配的對吧<br />\n親愛的<br />\n我的眼睛還在不停地流血呢<br />\n好暖和<br />\n就像當初妳的血噴灑在我的臉上一樣<br />\n親愛的妳那時候的表情真美<br />\n親愛的<br />\n我喜歡妳的血<br />\n親愛的<br />\n沒有心的妳安靜了好多<br />\n不再像從前那樣整天出去找他<br />\n以前妳很少像現在這樣陪我<br />\n妳只會對着他笑<br />\n我不會再讓妳去找他了<br />\n妳只可以愛我一個人<br />\n就像我愛你一樣<br />\n咦<br />\n那個男人好像就在這呢<br />\n怎麼辦<br />\n他還會搶走妳嗎<br />\n不可以<br />\n我不會讓妳離開我<br />\n親愛的<br />\n就讓我們一起<br />\n吃掉他吧<br />\n那個男人的味道怎麼樣<br />\n我一點也不喜歡<br />\n妳覺得呢<br />\n妳也討厭對吧...<br />\n<br />\n訓了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb0d206b4d83df76d2bdbd1599cf9d27bb1c8dc","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T22:28:59.000Z","msg":"如無意外嘅話7點會有文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61300d9d1783b5584364a4bed85d2533b60300bc","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T22:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如無意外嘅話7點會有文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夜晚7點"},{"pid":"c8651236884655dae9593f8162abd1e7946b1e44","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:22:43.000Z","msg":"自己推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a14b5623f44a695b850f9ead5f88f9fc290f2cb","tid":26302,"uid":30268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:25:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起樓上的房客嗰幕浴缸虐殺"},{"pid":"917efe3ce4801edf810dfbbba734e9785948d4d8","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:42:33.000Z","msg":"可妳不是說過妳最喜歡他嗎<br />\n那就都給妳吃好了<br />\n我把他剁碎了放在那裏<br />\n親愛的妳餓了就吃吧<br />\n親愛的妳實在是太安靜了<br />\n現在只有我們兩個人<br />\n那男人不會來打擾我們<br />\n可他的味道怎麼也散不去呢<br />\n他的血腥味散滿了整個屋子<br />\n真是討厭啊<br />\n咦<br />\n親愛的妳不吃他是因爲討厭他吧<br />\n我知道的<br />\n我會一點一點嚼碎他的骨頭<br />\n撕下他的肉<br />\n親愛的妳的手爲什麼這麼涼呢<br />\n我幫妳暖暖好不好<br />\n以前我就是這樣幫妳暖手的<br />\n妳說妳愛我<br />\n我至今都記得<br />\n可是他卻把妳搶走了<br />\n他也幫妳暖手嗎<br />\n親愛的<br />\n我有點難過<br />\n妳親親我好不好<br />\n一下就好...<br />\n<br />\n夜啲再出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba90885502e77225a305d4e0817d28436d1929fa","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:13:24.000Z","msg":"自己推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11eb25ec05038ad4349169e51b169ef60fb90e21","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"親愛的妳的脣也好涼<br />\n以前妳的脣是溫暖的<br />\n一切都變了<br />\n妳的心變了<br />\n妳的人也變了<br />\n但我不怪妳啊<br />\n都是那男人的錯對吧<br />\n我們都沒有錯<br />\n我真的好喜歡妳<br />\n無論妳做什麼我都會原諒妳<br />\n親愛的<br />\n天黑了嗎<br />\n我看不見了<br />\n妳當我的眼睛好嗎<br />\n以前妳會和我一起數星星<br />\n妳冷了我還會把外套給妳<br />\n妳現在全身都好涼啊<br />\n妳一定很冷吧<br />\n別擔心<br />\n我會抱着妳<br />\n如果天黑了<br />\n妳就替我看看月亮吧<br />\n在月光下我抱着妳<br />\n很浪漫不是嗎<br />\n<br />\n聽日先再出 幫小弟推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c2381ca819f96aa33135bc1477987bc747b22d","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:27:19.000Z","msg":"自己推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ead22bf66bc3174b0dbc6af33e00762bfb68b2","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n親愛的<br />\n妳喜歡我嗎<br />\n親愛的<br />\n我感覺越來越冷了<br />\n可是妳的身體比我還涼<br />\n別怕<br />\n我會緊緊抱住妳的<br />\n地上全是妳的血<br />\n粘了我一手<br />\n但只要是妳的我都喜歡<br />\n嗯 很甜<br />\n對不起<br />\n親愛的<br />\n我現在看不見妳了<br />\n只能用手描繪妳的面孔<br />\n不過妳放心<br />\n妳的模樣我永遠也不會忘記的<br />\n妳知道我有多愛妳嗎<br />\n親愛的<br />\n妳的臉上現在應該全是血吧<br />\n對不起<br />\n弄髒妳了<br />\n妳很在意自己的外貌的<br />\n而我卻一刀一刀割花了妳的臉<br />\n親愛的<br />\n別怪我<br />\n妳一定很生氣吧<br />\n我沒能讓你們天長地久<br />\n可是親愛的<br />\n妳要明白<br />\n這世上沒有人能比我更愛妳<br />\n我也想和妳天長地久<br />\n親愛的<br />\n求妳別拒絕我<br />\n我好討厭妳看他的眼神<br />\n所以我挖了妳的眼珠<br />\n親愛的妳別生氣<br />\n畢竟我把自己的眼珠給了妳不是嗎<br />\n其實這樣也好<br />\n因爲我一看見妳和他在一起就忍不住想把他撕碎<br />\n就像現在<br />\n他就在我眼前<br />\n但是我看不見他了<br />\n一想到他也看不見妳了<br />\n我好開心<br />\n妳只能是我的.....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c6043ceb1907d6751cee04473f2904844e084a","tid":26302,"uid":30268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T11:38:09.000Z","msg":"好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b65d27c12b6d76eb02eb2f4ad92ade77a08142","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:36:50.000Z","msg":"出去食飯 返黎再出 <br />\n推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c144f098d5a215e0c6665e3e3d716fc1582a528","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T14:15:09.000Z","msg":"親愛的<br />\n我真的好冷啊<br />\n風吹進我臉上的洞<br />\n我現在一定很丑吧<br />\n妳應該不會喜歡的<br />\n求妳別嫌棄我<br />\n我不知道應該怎麼做了<br />\n怎麼做妳才會愛我<br />\n親愛的<br />\n有陽光照進來了<br />\n周圍好吵啊<br />\n妳聽見了嗎<br />\n他們說是我殺了妳和他<br />\n他們都在罵我<br />\n明明是那個男人的錯對吧<br />\n爲什麼他們全都責備我<br />\n我好難過啊<br />\n親愛的<br />\n妳安慰我好嗎<br />\n只有妳不責備我了<br />\n親愛的<br />\n我被判刑了<br />\n聽他們說妳被火化了<br />\n和那個男人埋在一起<br />\n說什麼有情人被拆散<br />\n他們明明什麼都不懂<br />\n憑什麼說這些<br />\n我才是最愛妳的人<br />\n親愛的<br />\n我好想妳<br />\n呵<br />\n這樣真好<br />\n妳明白的<br />\n我不願意和任何人分享我的愛<br />\n他們全都不知道我愛妳<br />\n這樣我對妳的愛是完滿的對嗎<br />\n我想起了那年樹下的妳<br />\n妳對我笑了<br />\n如沐春風<br />\n親愛的<br />\n原諒我對妳的一見鍾情<br />\n從那一刻<br />\n我便愛上了妳<br />\n原諒我的自私<br />\n我不能忍受妳和任何人的曖昧<br />\n對不起<br />\n親愛的<br />\n最後是我親手毀了妳<br />\n我忘不了妳那時看我的眼神<br />\n可是我不得不這麼做<br />\n親愛的<br />\n妳大概永遠都不會知道<br />\n我有多愛妳<br />\n妳就是那樣的一個人<br />\n得之我幸<br />\n失之我命<br />\n如果從頭再來<br />\n我一定不會再愛上妳<br />\n不會再讓這樣髒的我毀了妳<br />\n但這輩子<br />\n我註定逃不開妳的劫<br />\n親愛的<br />\n妳要記住<br />\n我真的很愛妳<br />\n                   完<br />\n<br />\n推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7127c52539903c4a09816893655fa88836adf4","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T16:11:41.000Z","msg":"自己推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1564d0dcf21f42c60cfb6d4dc90551c91af021f","tid":26302,"uid":11062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T20:02:04.000Z","msg":"推推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e23026aa0b33b6d042489f69c61c36b617300a2c","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:42:18.000Z","msg":"自己推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252f1e406b44601bc0090f74d0b7372f8e5ffa95","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T20:17:02.000Z","msg":"自己推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5159543ee3d28ef777b97c2983bbf12301ebb781","tid":26302,"uid":3643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T22:23:41.000Z","msg":"幾鍾意最後一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575c129fee19c86b2ee1c71cef265f066dff9955","tid":26302,"uid":53185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:56:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾鍾意最後一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}